metadata.title: GLOBLELAND 200 Pcs Thank You Gift Tags Gold Foil Paper Gift Tags with 65.6ft Natural Jute Twine for Wedding Favors, Party Decor
features: Thank You Tags Pack: 200 pcs Thank You gift tags with 1 set 65.6 ft/ 20m natural jute rope. Rectangle label with real gold ink and gold foil printing.
High quality: Our gift tags are made of double-thick and durable paper, wrinkle-resistant and firm, easy to write, with natural jute twine, high-strength, and easy to knot.
Easy to Use: Each label has a pre-punched hole. You can pass the twine through the hole and tie it where you want.
Personalized DIY: One side of the label is printed with Thank You text, and the other side is blank. You can write your own wishes on the blank side to do personalized tags.
Widely Applications: Our gift wrap tags are very suitable for parties, people showers, weddings, anniversaries, graduation ceremonies, birthdays, wishing tree, DIY projects, etc.
description: GLOBLELAND Thank You Gift Wrap Tags Set Specifications Material: Paper Tags Size: 3 X 2 Inches/7.9 X 5 cm, 200 sheets Twine Size: 65.6 feet long, 1 pack Package Included 200 sheets of paper gift wrap tags 1 pack 65.6 feet of natural jute rope Widely Used Wedding Favors, Bridal Shower Favors, people Shower Favors, Birthday Party Favors, Guest Welcome Bags
